string-array.name: changelog
string-array.item: Now we have an extra app flavor with a dynamic clock! It will be only available on Github via Releases; check the readme in the GitHub repository for more info: https://github.com/Delta-Icons/android
APKs on GitHub are now named differently, so Obtanium users may have trouble receiveing updates (we apologize for that). There are fresh links for Obtanium in the GitHub readme!
